<tmc-service-inc>
<pub id="RM0251U">
<servcat id="36">
<name>BRAKE</name>
<section id="1000O_S0012" variety="S0012">
<name>PARKING BRAKE</name>
<ttl id="1000O_S0012_72V96_T0043" variety="T0043">
<name>PARKING BRAKE PEDAL</name>
<para id="RM0000022KK000X" category="A" type-id="8000E" name-id="PB09P-01" from="200601">
<name>REASSEMBLY</name>
<subpara id="RM0000022KK000X_01" type-id="01" category="01">
<s-1 id="RM0000022KK000X_01_0001" proc-id="RM0250U___00003P800000">
<ptxt>INSTALL PARKING PEDAL PAD</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<s2>
<ptxt>Install the parking pedal pad to the parking brake pedal assembly.</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="C132702" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
</s2>
</content1>
</s-1>
<s-1 id="RM0000022KK000X_01_0002" proc-id="RM0250U___00003P900000">
<ptxt>INSTALL PARKING BRAKE SWITCH ASSEMBLY</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<s2>
<ptxt>Install the parking brake switch assembly with the screw.</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="C132700" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
</s2>
</content1>
</s-1>
<s-1 id="RM0000022KK000X_01_0003" proc-id="RM0250U___00003PA00000">
<ptxt>INSTALL NO. 1 PARKING BRAKE CABLE ASSEMBLY</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<s2>
<ptxt>Pass the No. 1 parking brake cable assembly through the pedal guide.</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="C143747E01" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Using a brass bar and a hammer, install the clip to the No. 1 parking brake cable assembly.</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Temporarily tighten the the lock nut and No. 1 wire adjusting nut.</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="C132697" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
<atten3>
<ptxt>Fully tighten the lock nut and the No. 1 wire adjusting nut when adjusting the parking brake pedal travel.</ptxt>
</atten3>
<torque>
<torqueitem>
<t-value1>5.4</t-value1>
<t-value2>55</t-value2>
<t-value3>48</t-value3>
</torqueitem>
</torque>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Bend the parking brake pedal claw.</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="C132699" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
</s2>
</content1>
</s-1>
</subpara>
</para>
</ttl>
</section>
</servcat>
</pub>
</tmc-service-inc>